												<img src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/e68bd5ce6096e171bc23783422e89c7d?d=http://tastykitchen.com/recipes/wp-content/plugins/buddypress/bp-core/images/mystery-man.jpg&amp;s=68" alt="Avatar Image" class="avatar user-28515-avatar" width='68' height='68' />						<div class="recipe-title">
							<h1  itemprop="name">Frozen Hot Chocolate</h1>
							<p class="by">by <a href="http://tastykitchen.com/recipes/members/wehearawho/"><span itemprop="author">MamaFoodie</span></a> on February 21, 2010 in <a href="http://tastykitchen.com/recipes/category/drinks/" title="View all posts in Drinks" rel="category tag">Drinks</a>, <a href="http://tastykitchen.com/recipes/category/drinks/smoothies/" title="View all posts in Smoothies" rel="category tag">Smoothies</a></p>
<p class="related-link"><a target="_blank" onClick="javascript: firstTracker._trackPageview('/outbound/recipes/http://mamafoodie.com/?p=299');"   href="http://mamafoodie.com/?p=299" class="recipe-source">See this recipe post on MamaFoodie&rsquo;s site!</a></p>							<span style="display:none;" itemprop="published" datetime="2010-02-21">February 21, 2010</span>
							<span style='display:none;' itemprop='recipeType'>Drinks</span><span style='display:none;' itemprop='recipeType'>Smoothies</span>						</div> <!-- end recipe-title -->
