											<p>Oh man. This is so good. As in, I&#8217;m now going to have to buy a gym membership good. It&#8217;s been a few years since I&#8217;ve been to Serendipity, but when I went with some friends, the Peanut Butter Frrozen Hot Chocolate was the favorite. I&#8217;ve made this twice now. The first time I followed the recipe exactly, except I subbed half &amp; half for the evaporated milk. The second time I added in a scoop of peanut butter and a sprinkling of sea salt. WOW. Imagine all the other possibilities, like raspberry or caramel syrup. Add lots of ice cubes, I added the whole tray for two servings.</p>
